🌟 Calling all Women in Law! 🌟

Ready to reclaim your well-being and prioritize your health? Join us for the EmpowerHer Retreat, a rejuvenating wellness experience crafted exclusively for women in the legal profession.

📅 Save the Date: Saturday, May 18th
🕣 Time: 8:30 AM - 2:00 PM
📍 Location: Atha Yoga, Delray Beach
💲 Price: $147 Early Bird until April 22nd

Hosted by Rising Nature Retreats & Flourish Law Group, this day retreat is mindfully designed to nourish your mind, body, and soul amidst the serene ambiance of Atha Yoga’s South Florida outdoor oasis.

Here’s what’s waiting for you:

🧘‍♀️ Yoga, Meditation & Sound Healing Sessions
💬 Wellness Expert Discussion Panel
🎤 Keynote Speaker: Lauren Klein @lawyerlaurenklein from Flourish Law Group, sharing her inspiring journey of overcoming burnout and cultivating a fulfilling career
🥗 Delicious Vegetarian Lunch
🤝 Community Connection and Guided Discussion & Journaling

Don’t miss out on this empowering opportunity to invest in yourself and ignite positive change in your life. 

Reserve your spot today on RisingNatureRetreats.com and embark on a transformational journey at the EmpowerHer Retreat! ✨🌿 #linkinbio
